[The MMWR Update under-reports the number of confirmed equine cases. The
USDA-APHIS update of Mon 15 Oct 2001 (see: West Nile virus surveillance
2001 - USA (26) 20011018--) identifies 191 confirmed equine cases
distributed through 15 states. In addition a fifth and sixth human case
were reported in New Jersey on 13 Oct 2001 (see: West Nile virus, human -
USA (New Jersey) (02) 20011016.2541), which makes the total number of human
cases 33. - Mod.CP
